Planned 4 PRs:

1. Runtime reload + plugin skills + hook parity callsites.
2. Marketplace registry/update + plugin update/enable/disable.
3. Routines + dynamic workflow primitives.
4. Messaging-core ratchet notification-event bridge.

## First PR Must Include

- plugin daemon retention/shutdown fix;
- daemon plugin reload primitive and CLI entrypoint;
- plugin skills visible in `ratchet skill list/show`;
- explicit skill mention injection for chat prompts;
- hook events/calls for user prompt submit, pre/post tool use, permission request/denied, pre/post compact, stop/stop-failure, and error;
